name: TravelReport
0:

”how long will it take to get from Washington D.C. to Pittsburgh?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: travel report
des:
Travel Report gives you an estimated travel time using current live data.

Just ask:

"Alexa, ask Travel Report how long will it take to get from {Point A} to {Point B}?"

Examples:

"Alexa, ask Travel Report how long will it take from Richmond Virginia to McLean Virginia?"

"Alexa, ask Travel Report how is it from 7900 Westpark Drive, Virginia to Tysons Mall, Virginia?"

"Alexa, open Travel Report. How long will it take to get from Washington D.C. to Pittsburgh?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
